 of our dataset, to be suitable to rank the SMI\nseries that we have analyzed in three distinct groups.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Jul 2015 10:05:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 31 Oct 2015 12:05:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 29 May 2017 08:05:05 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 12 Jun 2017 09:42:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-13"}
